{"tid":1874773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世衛：武漢肺炎對支那以外地區構成重大威脅","createTime":"2020-02-11T11:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T13:32:11.000Z","uid":125168,"like":34,"dislike":142,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"43d15e7c06a2c1bcf3cbfcebedc905d4be927387","tid":1874773,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:27:23.000Z","msg":"世衛警告疫情對中國以外地區構成重大威脅<br />\n2分鐘前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情持續擴散，世界衛生組織警告疫情對中國以外地區構成重大威脅。<br />\n<br />\n內地至今有42667人確診染病，死亡個案增至1016宗，港澳台確診個案就增至合共77宗。<br />\n<br />\n全球其他地區確診病例合共三百多宗，最多的是日本、新加坡、泰國。世衛總幹事譚德塞在討論新型肺炎的國際視像會議中指出，雖然病例九成九出現在中國，但對全球其他地方亦是嚴重威脅，他呼籲各國共享病毒樣本和加快研究治療藥物與疫苗。"},{"pid":"44d1c2d234834cbbcbe10d286b84ca1624f9b666","tid":1874773,"uid":125168,"like":153,"dislike":1,"score":152,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:28:20.000Z","msg":"全世界都無視世衛做曬防疫工作，而家先黎扮嘢有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1daf536877d76f4e054fcc3cecafc5080d9957f","tid":1874773,"uid":80724,"like":193,"dislike":0,"score":193,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:28:57.000Z","msg":"重慢撚過IE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8d662164b11237471531abe3420235a4e5a029","tid":1874773,"uid":164477,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"因為無人捐錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282aa5357460b6e7e0fbf3025c899343194436ba","tid":1874773,"uid":293012,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"求搵人組隊隊冧垃圾呃人日本代購page<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1874768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1874768</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nChing唔好意思，借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e8660ed817b2e3787865885757afa311817e9f"